# Page Redesign Plan & Implementation Strategy

This plan outlines the structural and aesthetic changes to be made across the CampusShare platform, preserving all backend logic, API contracts, and database schemas.

## User Review Required
> [!IMPORTANT]
> Please review this redesign plan. We are changing the structural layout and styling of key pages. No backend or database changes will be made. **Do you approve this proposal so we can begin the implementation phase?**

## Proposed Changes

### Global Architecture
- **CSS Variables**: Update [globals.css](file:///c:/Upendra/Git%20Hub/Git%20Hub%20--%20Kolla%20Upendra/campusshare/src/app/globals.css) with the new design system tokens (Brand Indigo, pure white cards, soft pearl backgrounds).
- **Layout Shell ([AppShell.tsx](file:///c:/Upendra/Git%20Hub/Git%20Hub%20--%20Kolla%20Upendra/campusshare/src/components/layout/AppShell.tsx))**: Refine spacing and ensure the `BottomNav` integrates seamlessly without overlapping content.

---

### Landing Page ([/page.tsx](file:///c:/Upendra/Git%20Hub/Git%20Hub%20--%20Kolla%20Upendra/campusshare/src/app/page.tsx))
- **Current Issues**: Center-heavy layout, static feel, generic button hierarchy.
- **New Layout**: 
  - **Desktop**: Split hero section. Bold, left-aligned typography with a dynamic visual (staggered UI cards) on the right.
  - **Mobile**: Clean, punchy hero with full-width primary CTA.
  - **Features**: Convert the 3-column feature grid to a more engaging masonry or alternating layout.
- **Component Reuse**: `Button`, new `FeatureCard` component.

### Dashboard ([/dashboard/page.tsx](file:///c:/Upendra/Git%20Hub/Git%20Hub%20--%20Kolla%20Upendra/campusshare/src/app/dashboard/page.tsx))
- **Current Issues**: Clunky native `<select>` filters, sticky header takes up too much vertical space, generic empty state.
- **New Layout**:
  - **Search & Filters**: Replace the native dropdowns with a sleek horizontal scrolling row of "Chips" (segmented control) for Categories. 
  - **Grid**: Optimized aspect ratios for [ItemCard](file:///c:/Upendra/Git%20Hub/Git%20Hub%20--%20Kolla%20Upendra/campusshare/src/components/items/ItemCard.tsx#31-93) to prevent aggressive image cropping.
  - **Empty State**: Beautiful illustrated empty state indicating "No items found".
- **Performance**: Optimize images on cards, ensure rendering is clean.

### Item Card ([/components/items/ItemCard.tsx](file:///c:/Upendra/Git%20Hub/Git%20Hub%20--%20Kolla%20Upendra/campusshare/src/components/items/ItemCard.tsx))
- **Current Issues**: Equal weight given to title and price. Takes up too much space for action buttons.
- **New Layout**: 
  - Highlight the price with the primary or accent color.
  - Use a subtle glassmorphism or soft shadow (`shadow-sm hover:shadow-md`).
  - Smooth scale animation on the image (`hover:scale-105 duration-500`).

### Authentication ([/auth/signin/page.tsx](file:///c:/Upendra/Git%20Hub/Git%20Hub%20--%20Kolla%20Upendra/campusshare/src/app/auth/signin/page.tsx))
- **Current Issues**: Extremely barebones, missing trust signals.
- **New Layout**: 
  - **Desktop**: Split screen design. Left side features an inspiring campus/student graphic or a rotating testimonial. Right side contains the centered login card.
  - **Mobile**: Elevated card with subtle background blur and a vibrant logo presentation.

### Post Item ([/post-item/page.tsx](file:///c:/Upendra/Git%20Hub/Git%20Hub%20--%20Kolla%20Upendra/campusshare/src/app/post-item/page.tsx) & `AddItemForm.tsx`)
- **Current Issues**: Basic vertical form lacking strong contextual grouping.
- **New Layout**:
  - Group fields logically into "Cards" (e.g., *Basic Details*, *Pricing*, *Images*).
  - Modernize the image upload zone into a dashed dropzone with thumbnail previews.
  - Ensure clear inline validation states (red borders, helper text) instead of relying solely on toasts.

### Item Details (`/items/[id]/page.tsx` - extrapolated)
- **Current Issues**: Standard vertical stack.
- **New Layout**:
  - **Desktop**: 2-column layout. Image gallery on the left, sticky booking/action card on the right (similar to Airbnb).
  - **Mobile**: Full-width swipeable image gallery at the top, with a rounded bottom-sheet style content area overlapping the images slightly.

